Nero Express v10 [Lite Edition Repacked/Precracked].
This is Nero Express v10 with OPTIONAL Nero Info Tool and Nero Cover Designer.
It requires between 120MB and 200MB of your HDD.


Installation instructions:

1. Run &quot;Nero Express v10 [Lite Edition Repacked].exe&quot;.
2. Install.
3. On Desktop, two icons (files) will be shown: Nero Serial Installation and Nero ControlCenter.
4. Open Nero Control Center and look for the License Tab and click on ADD.
5. Open the Nero Serial and copy/paste key onto empty space and click NEXT.
6. I don't recommend you to download any addiotional plugins, just click on NEXT and CLOSE or QUIT....whatever.
7. You should delete those two icons from desktop (Nero Serial Installation and Nero ControlCenter) and create shortcut for Nero Express on Desktop.


Nero is now activated and ready for burning.

Tested on Windows XP x86, Vista/7 both x86 and x64.




Enjoy and seed.


